The paper proposes a novel framework for dealing with long-tailed distribution in classification tasks using deep Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs). This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), and Multimedia (cs.MM). Among these, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely categories as they are directly related to the proposed method.
